org.spongycastle.crypto.digests

Class SHA224Digest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spongycastle.crypto.digests.GeneralDigest
      • org.spongycastle.crypto.digests.SHA224Digest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Digest, ExtendedDigest

    public class SHA224Digest
extends GeneralDigest
    SHA-224 as described in RFC 3874 
             block  word  digest
 SHA-1   512    32    160
 SHA-224 512    32    224
 SHA-256 512    32    256
 SHA-384 1024   64    384
 SHA-512 1024   64    512

        Parameters:
